      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several visible scratches, a few small dents, and some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin shows signs of regular use with some wear on the seats and carpets, though all essential features like the AC and radio are working perfectly. While it is mechanically sound and has a clear service history, a buyer should expect the typical wear-and-tear associated with a well-used vehicle.",
