      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been meticulously garaged and maintained to a standard rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior boasts a flawless, deep-gloss paint finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium upholstery remains taut with zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and the interior still retains that signature new-car aroma. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the bespoke infotainment system, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, featuring a full, documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is show-room clean, and the undercarriage is free of any debris or oxidation. This is a turn-key investment for a buyer who demands perfection and a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
